The Smokehouse Gas Smoker has just this range and with the smallest brass burner in the industry, the smoker impresses while holding low temps and not having the burner blow out in the wind. The 14,500 BTU brass burner isn’t shy about cranking up the heat either. At 500 degrees F you can be smoking dozens of hamburgers at once for your BBQ cookout. Ribs? Brisket? Jerky? Sausage? Steaks? Turkeys? No problem with this versatile smoker! The premium rotary igniter starts the smoker instantly. For your wood, the flame centered wood box can burn everything from wood chips to wood chunks to BBQ pellets, and the lid is properly vented to release all the smoke you’d want. The cabinet itself is constructed of sturdy, heavy duty steel with side steel handles and a fully insulated door that has a magnetic latch. Inside, you’ll have a 635 square inch cooking area with four adjustable chrome-plated steel cooking grills that are dishwasher safe and easy to clean. Below the grills sits a water/drip pan where you can place your favorite apple juice blend for your ribs or just use it to catch all the drippings.Smokehouse Products Outdoor Gas Smoker/Cooker - Silver

Condition : This item is brand new, unopened and sealed in its original factory box.
